, these results are consistent with the hypothesis that\n              A. fistulata\n              evolved its remarkable tongue in a coevolutionary race with long-tubed flowers similar to that envisioned by Darwin.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Muchhala, Nathan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Thomson, James D.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/9d83dff873e4a89ffe687cd29ec9a38d", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/53a1a916426dd79e61d3e9d964a1a727b04c839b81f9c962af55f2ee77f7b6ee", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/CXATKIWP", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/CXATKIWP", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/db12e930a6e99b4543fb45686d271bba!/b286282-288763", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1665", "pages": "2147-2152", "title": "Proceedings of the Royal Society B: Biological Sciences", "volume": "276"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/9d83dff873e4a89ffe687cd29ec9a38d"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:CXATKIWP"}, {"identifier": "10.1098/rspb.2009.0102"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent"